author: PTI
title: West Bengal says it will abide by lockdown order
description: West Bengal says it will abide by lockdown orderThe assurance came hours after the Centre accused the Mamata Banerjee-led West Bengal government of obstructing a Central team deputed to assess the coronavirus ground situation.
content:
NEW DELHI: The West Bengal government has said "it is not a fact" that there was no cooperation with the Central team deputed to assess the COVID-19 situation in the state and gave an assurance that it will abide by all Union government orders on lockdown.
